OL,3,CWoman fined after miscarriage calls
OL,4,Cnew baby loss certificates 'pointless'
OL,6,FMs Hawkes : "I rang them up straight
OL,7,Faway - explained I've lost my baby and
OL,8,Fassumed they'll say 'that's fine,
OL,9,Fdon't worry'.
OL,11,F"But I was told to get a doctor's note
OL,12,F- which was traumatic."
OL,14,FNow, the NHS Business Service
OL,15,FAuthority has told ITV News Calendar
OL,16,Fthat the new baby loss certificates
OL,17,Fare not legal documents, so they
OL,18,Fcannot be used to prove pregnancy and
OL,19,Ftherefore waive a fine.
