OL,3,CWoman fined after miscarriage calls
OL,4,Cnew baby loss certificates 'pointless'
OL,6,FThe new certificates, introduced by
OL,7,Fthe Department of Health to recognise
OL,8,Fthe grief of mothers who lose babies
OL,9,Fbefore 24 weeks of pregnancy, can be
OL,10,Fclaimed by anyone and are not signed
OL,11,Fby a health professional.
OL,13,FMs Hakwes, from Otley, said: "What is
OL,14,Fthe point? They've taken time to make
OL,15,Fthese certificates - why not make them
OL,16,Finto legal documents so they can be
OL,17,Fused where you haven't been able to
OL,18,Fget an exemption certificate?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
