OL,3,CWoman fined after miscarriage calls
OL,4,Cnew baby loss certificates 'pointless'
OL,6,F"This has really spurred me on,
OL,7,Fbecause the fines happen to so many
OL,8,Fwomen - and they should just not be
OL,9,Fgoing through this."
OL,11,FShe's now setting up a petition
OL,12,Fcalling for the NHS to make the
OL,13,Fcertificates legally binding.
OL,15,FMs Hawkes added: "You can't claim the
OL,16,Fexemption certificates once you've had
OL,17,Fa miscarriage and so many people lose
OL,18,Ftheir baby before they get them at
OL,19,Ftheir midwife appointment."
