OL,3,CWoman fined after miscarriage calls
OL,4,Cnew baby loss certificates 'pointless'
OL,6,FResearch has shown as many as one in
OL,7,Fthree pregnant women never receive an
OL,8,Fexemption certificate.
OL,10,FAn ITV News Calendar investigation
OL,11,Fshowed that in 2022, more than 24,000
OL,12,Fwomen were sent letters demanding
OL,13,Fpayment for prescriptions because they
OL,14,Fhad failed to provide evidence of a
OL,15,Fpregnancy.
OL,17,FAnother woman who did not get her
OL,18,Fcertificate was Nicola Good from
OL,19,FLeeds. She is still fighting a fine
OL,20,Fmore than a year after miscarrying.
