OL,3,CWoman fined after miscarriage calls
OL,4,Cnew baby loss certificates 'pointless'
OL,6,FShe said: "I think they must get the
OL,7,Fidea that I am not going to be paying
OL,8,Fit. I was pregnant, I provided
OL,9,Fevidence and I feel like I've been
OL,10,Fdiscriminated against for miscarrying.
OL,12,F"The certificates are good to help
OL,13,Fwith processing grief, but if it's not
OL,14,Fgoing to put an end to the crazy fine
OL,15,Fsystem then that feels stupid."
