OL,3,CWoman fined after miscarriage calls
OL,4,Cnew baby loss certificates 'pointless'
OL,6,FNicola's MP Kim Leadbeater, who has
OL,7,Fpreviously campaigned for maternity
OL,8,Fexemption certificates to be claimed
OL,9,Fretrospectively, said: "I welcome the
OL,10,Fintroduction of the certificate - it's
OL,11,Fan important acknowledgement that
OL,12,Fpeople lost a baby, and what they go
OL,13,Fthrough.
OL,15,F"But what these certificates don't do
OL,16,Fis acknowledge the problem around
OL,17,Fpaying for prescriptions. So it's
OL,18,Factually made people like Nicola
OL,19,Funderstandably more angry and upset."
