OL,3,CWoman fined after miscarriage calls
OL,4,Cnew baby loss certificates 'pointless'
OL,6,FIn a statement, the NHS Business
OL,7,FService Authority said: "Baby loss
OL,8,Fcertificates were introduced by the
OL,9,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,10,Fto recognise parents' grief and loss.
OL,12,F"Certificates are official but not
OL,13,Flegal documents, and whilst they
OL,14,Fprovide recognition of loss, because
OL,15,Fthe certificates are a voluntary self-
OL,16,Fdeclaration they can't be used as
OL,17,Fevidence to remove a penalty charge.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
